The Item Card includes:

* Alcohol degree, Year, Sugar, Bottle Volume etc..

* Using EOS Wine Item Tracking Code is mandatory.

* Lot No. Formula. This field allows the Lot No. Calculation:

	- DD = Day

	- DDD = Julian Day

	- MM = Month

	- WW = Week

	- Y = Year
	
	- HH = Hour

	- MI = Minutes